Class JonixFilesExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.stream.JonixExtractor
      • com.tectonica.jonix.stream.JonixFilesExtractor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JonixRawExtractor, JonixUnifiedExtractor, Onix2Extractor, Onix3Extractor

    public abstract class JonixFilesExtractor
extends JonixExtractor
    Simple extension of JonixExtractor adding events related for file-processing, fired by a JonixFilesStreamer. Doesn't add any new abstract methods, hence puts no additional burden compared to sub-classing from JonixExtractor.
    Author:
    Zach Melamed
